characterDescription:
Zuln is a female Dullform Parshendi who serves on their ruling council, the Council of Five, in their city of Narak.
She has indicated that she considers it her duty to represent those with no songs, along with any dullforms among them. Hers is as noble a sacrifice as that of Abronai holding to mateform.

characterDetails.Appearance: She wears the smock of a parshman.
